    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税“死亡表”使华尔街面临严酷的现实</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国投资者班级＆Mdash; 拥有几乎所有股票的前10％; 在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易攻势时代，很快就会遵守其新的，艰巨的地位。从企业高管将其股票期权计算到亿万富翁对冲基金大亨以及介于两者之间的每个人，现在只是附带损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-tariff-chart-how-stock-market-crash-hits-wall-street-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 21:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西中央银行负责人会与银行家会面，作为贷方teeters</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/brazil-central-bank-head-meets-with-bankers-as-a-lender-teeters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西中央银行总裁加布里埃尔·加里波洛（Gabriel Galipolo）在周末与顶级银行家会面，因为他们试图减轻销售Banco Master SA的影响，Banco Master SA是一家较小的银行，该银行在美国金融安全网的支持下迅速发展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/brazil-central-bank-head-meets-with-bankers-as-a-lender-teeters</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 20:07:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队拒绝市场恐惧，预测关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-team-rejects-market-fears-projecting-defiance-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的高级经济官员驳斥了投资者对通货膨胀和衰退的恐惧，对全球关税席卷全球关税引发的市场动荡并没有道歉，并坚持坚持繁荣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/trump-team-rejects-market-fears-projecting-defiance-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 20:07:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>飙升的关税让奇异果的投资者将测试2020年低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/soaring-tariffs-have-investors-concerned-kiwi-will-test-2020-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对全球贸易战争和冒险情绪的越来越多的担忧使一些投资者担心新西兰美元将在年底时测试其COVID时代的低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/soaring-tariffs-have-investors-concerned-kiwi-will-test-2020-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国库明星是避风港，即使特朗普的球迷停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/treasuries-star-as-haven-bet-even-as-trump-fans-stagflation-woes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[震惊的投资者正在担心唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易战争将引发全球衰退，并占据美国国债。至少目前忽略相同的惩罚性关税可能会释放出另一回合通货膨胀的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/treasuries-star-as-haven-bet-even-as-trump-fans-stagflation-woes</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特斯拉公牛（Tesla Bull</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/tesla-bull-slashes-stock-price-target-43-citing-musk-and-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街最看涨的特斯拉公司之一的分析师之一将其对该股票的价格目标降低了43％，理由是首席执行官埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）和美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易政策造成的品牌危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/tesla-bull-slashes-stock-price-target-43-citing-musk-and-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 18:44:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Evercore ISI是华尔街最新的公司，可削减S＆amp; P 500目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/evercore-isi-is-latest-firm-on-wall-street-to-cut-s-p-500-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在S＆amp; P 500指数在短短两天内就消除了5.4万亿美元的贸易战争恐惧后，Evercore ISI加入了其他华尔街公司，表示在2025年的目标和Mdash中过于乐观。但是仍然看到股票按年底划分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/evercore-isi-is-latest-firm-on-wall-street-to-cut-s-p-500-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 15:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>夏天警告5.4万亿美元的溃败后有更多的动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/summers-warns-of-more-turbulence-ahead-after-5-4-trillion-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场很有可能会看到与周四和周五发生的事情相似的动荡，前财政部长劳伦斯·萨默斯（Lawrence Summers）在X周日的帖子中写道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/summers-warns-of-more-turbulence-ahead-after-5-4-trillion-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 14:51:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南提议在特朗普采取行动后删除对我们的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/vietnam-offers-to-remove-all-tariffs-on-us-after-trump-action</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据越南共产党的一封信，越南提出在唐纳德·特朗普总统宣布对东南亚国家的46％征税后，旨在取消对美国进口的所有关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/vietnam-offers-to-remove-all-tariffs-on-us-after-trump-action</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 12:52:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度寻求美国贸易谈判，表明没有报复性关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/india-to-focus-on-trade-deal-avoids-retaliation-on-us-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度政府表示，这不会针对美国征收互惠关税采取报复性行动，而是将努力集中在与特朗普政府达成双边贸易协定以降落职责上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/india-to-focus-on-trade-deal-avoids-retaliation-on-us-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 09:25:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
